               <p>Indicted in a second COUNT for that she on the 11th of August, in the 29th year of his Majesty's reign by the Name of Maria Jones did marry the said 
               <persName id="t17940917-10-person241">
                  George
                   Edkins
               <interp inst="t17940917-10-person241" type="surname" value="Edkins"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940917-10-person241" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940917-10-person241" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , and that being so married afterwards on the 6th of April last, in the parish of St. James's, Clerkenwell, feloniously did marry and take to husband 
               <persName id="t17940917-10-person242">
                  James
                   Slark
               <interp inst="t17940917-10-person242" type="surname" value="Slark"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940917-10-person242" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940917-10-person242" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , the said George Edkins, her former husband, being alive.(The case opened by Mr. Knowlys.)</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17940917-10-person243">
                  SAMUEL
                   BRIDE
               <interp inst="t17940917-10-person243" type="surname" value="BRIDE"></interp>
