                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am the parish clerk of St. James's, Westminster; I have the register of the marriage with me of 
               <persName id="t17940917-10-person244">
                  George
                   Edkins
               <interp inst="t17940917-10-person244" type="surname" value="Edkins"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940917-10-person244" type="given" value="George"></interp>
